Job Description:

  Assist in designing marketing plans and implementing strategic sales to achieve company objectives
  Develop and optimize presentation document and commercial proposal
  Maintain and develop client relationship
  Organize internal meetings to discuss tendering projects
  Prepare and organize relevant parties to attend external meetings with clients
  Work with Internal teams to follow up project issues and solve clients’ problems
  Give prompt feedback to clients’ enquiries
  Report to Marketing Manager


Requirement:

  Good problem solving and communication skills
  Must be hard working and be able to work under pressure
  Proficient with Microsoft office, especially excellent PowerPoint skills is a must
  Prioritize candidate familiar with construction market
